'''奶油煮蛋配吐司'''（Creamed eggs on toast）在[[美國|美國]]是早餐菜色。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=w1Y5AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA435 Good Housekeeping] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=w1Y5AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA435 |date=20191001110800 }}. p. 435.</ref> [[吐司|吐司]]或[[面饼|比斯吉]]澆上[[白醬|白醬]]做的肉汁<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=PsVC5fzo2eYC&pg=PA36 Entertaining on the Jewish Holidays - Israela Banin] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=PsVC5fzo2eYC&pg=PA36 |date=20191001045456 }}. p. 36.</ref>和切碎的[[水煮蛋|水煮蛋]]。肉汁可以添加各種調味，例如：[[黑胡椒|黑胡椒]]、蒜粉、芹菜鹽、[[伍斯特醬|伍斯特醬]]、[[雪莉酒|雪利酒]]、[[香芹|香芹]]碎和／或[[蝦夷蔥|蝦夷蔥]]碎。

《[[廚藝之樂|廚藝之樂]]》一書中建議用鮮奶油及雞高湯各半製作白醬，並添加酸豆或碎醃瓜。<ref name="Joy">{{Cite book|title=Joy of Cooking|url=https://archive.org/details/joyofcooking300romb|last=Rombauer|first=Irma S.|last2=Becker, Marion Rombauer|date=1975|publisher=Bobbs-Merrill|isbn=0-672-51831-7|edition=Enlarged and rev.|location=Indianapolis|page=[https://archive.org/details/joyofcooking300romb/page/342 342]}}</ref>顏色較淺的醬汁常會加一點[[辣椒粉|辣椒粉]]或卡宴辣椒做點綴，這道菜也不例外。

奶油煮蛋配吐司也常用來清剩菜，加入碎火腿、小牛肉、雞肉、龍蝦、煮過的蘆筍和豌豆等配料也不少見。<ref name="Fannie">{{Cite book|title=The Fannie Farmer Cookbook|url=https://archive.org/details/fanniefarmercook00farm|last=Perkins|first=Wilma Lord|date=1965|publisher=Little, Brown and Co|edition=11th|page=[https://archive.org/details/fanniefarmercook00farm/page/102 102]}}</ref>

「黃花蛋（Eggs Goldenrod）」是奶油煮蛋配土司的變種：先將水煮蛋的蛋黃取出，碎蛋白和吐司澆上白醬後灑上碎蛋黃。<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Original Boston Cooking-School Cook Book, 1896|url=https://archive.org/details/originalbostonco0000farm_f4q4|last=Farmer|first=Fannie Merritt|date=1996|publisher=H.L. Levin Associates|isbn=0-88363-196-2|edition=100th anniversary|location=[New York]|page=[https://archive.org/details/originalbostonco0000farm_f4q4/page/96 96]}}</ref> 另有一道稱為「Eggs à la Bechamel」的菜餚：以奶油煎麵包丁取代吐司；水波蛋或半熟蛋取代水煮蛋，<ref name="Escoffier">{{Cite book|title=The new Larousse gastronomique : the encyclopedia of food, wine & cookery|url=https://archive.org/details/newlaroussegastr00mont|last=editor|first=Prosper Montagné ; American|last2=Escoffier, Charlotte Turgeon|last3=pref. by Robert J. Courtine|last4=original preface by Auguste|last5=Hunter, Philéas Gilbert|last6=text translated from the French by Marion|date=1977|publisher=Crown Publishers|isbn=0-517-53137-2|location=New York|page=[https://archive.org/details/newlaroussegastr00mont/page/344 344]}}</ref> 最後把蛋置於麵包丁上，淋上醬汁。

奶油煮蛋配吐司是很多家庭復活節早午餐的傳統菜。這道菜第一次出現在1896年Fanny Farmer所寫的《Boston Cooking-School Cook Book 》，每個人從自己籃子裡取出兩顆復活節彩蛋當奶油煮蛋的材料；彩蛋上各種顏色會暈染在白色的肉汁上，更為這道菜增添節慶色彩。

